{"tid":757880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爭地5男女群毆　婦爆頭重創","createTime":"2018-07-27T07:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T09:26:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c396efb8e0cce6002b655518b6bf59572269a7be","tid":757880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180727/20461445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F20461445&d=rHN6vsleqB0umXlyQsQjUttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f6897ba6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F20461445&h=313f644c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180727/20461445</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月27日 <br />\n<br />\n爭地5男女群毆　婦爆頭重創<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180727/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180727%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=ee5830a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■頭部重創女子送院搶救（左圖），另一男子報稱受傷，由警員押至醫院（右圖）。溫文學攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一對男女昨傍晚在荃灣老圍村與3名男女，疑為爭用一塊農地問題發生爭吵後，雙方拿起木棍及鐵通互相追打，結果5人同告受傷，其中一名女子頭部被扑中重創昏迷，送院搶救後要在深切治療部留醫。警員到場調查後，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架拘捕涉案5男女。<br />\n<br />\n51歲重傷女子姓陳，與68歲姓梁男傷者為一夥；另一方2女1男傷者分別姓羅（34歲）、姓張（63歲）及姓羅（68歲）。現場為荃灣老圍村同和街一塊位於斜坡下的農地，農地四周有以建築廢材搭建的圍欄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留醫深切治療部<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，陳女一方及涉案3男女均聲稱獲地主同意使用該塊農地。昨傍晚6時許，男女事主在農地內，突然有3名男女闖入，事主阻止，雙方先是口角繼而動武，有人取起木棍及鐵通互相追打，混亂中女事主疑遭對方用鐵通重擊頭部，當場昏倒地上。<br />\n<br />\n警員及救護員接報到場，將女事主送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，在深切治療部留醫；其餘4人亦報稱受傷送院。警方調查後，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將5人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫瑞麟、溫文學  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n投資「方特幣」逾50人受騙"},{"pid":"2bcd16e44f893e2a99fe37141f72c5208d24bb43","tid":757880,"uid":13802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"加埋幾百歲 醜死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40288fbfccd19dddab2406ef46e0c9add26cb3e6","tid":757880,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"死左咪唔駛爭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a8973814e4374eab1eab0a724f4967fd95c623","tid":757880,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"一個死<br />\n<br />\n其他坐監<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b754b242677938479866259ec88dfd69cc4e0e62","tid":757880,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}